{"tid":1906533,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"金希澈: 不會對女友撒嬌，想展現帥氣的形象","createTime":"2020-03-02T04:17:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T04:52:52.000Z","uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c460e2ca74aeff586eecf1c19d2fe6069607c0ab","tid":1906533,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:17:25.000Z","msg":"金希澈&ldquo;不會對女友撒嬌，想展現帥氣的形象&rdquo;<br />\n最近在錄製JTBC《77億的愛情》中的《請偏袒我》環節時，節目公開了因愛撒嬌的女朋友而苦惱的男人的故事。<br />\n<br />\n隨後，金希澈與77青春男女一起談起了戀人的撒嬌的話題，還用可愛的聲音說：&quot;想你了，快來吧~~&quot;展現了撒嬌，讓錄製現場頓時充滿了粉紅色的氣氛。<br />\n<br />\n錄製中，金希澈羞澀地說道：&quot;事實上，我不會對女朋友撒嬌，想向她展現帥氣的男人形象。&quot;展現了反轉魅力。該節目將於韓國時間2日晚11時播出。<br />\n<br />\n希澈老師好型...上埋戀愛節目"},{"pid":"96260d5810643daa9043cc8abd2434f877a8388b","tid":1906533,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:18:05.000Z","msg":"Ok型嘅..."},{"pid":"ba6ab472ba286d1a8a33b24478d7bf7016e6efc8","tid":1906533,"uid":229026,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:18:44.000Z","msg":"撒嬌唔緊要 唔好撒謊就得啦😢"},{"pid":"273b605aac91aeb5c4f75605cdad7613648edf86","tid":1906533,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96260d5810643daa9043cc8abd2434f877a8388b","tid":1906533,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:18:05.000Z","msg":"Ok型嘅..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:22:06.000Z","msg":"黑轉粉?"},{"pid":"11cb94c309318c1d8457c1caa54380bbd0e4a0e7","tid":1906533,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"273b605aac91aeb5c4f75605cdad7613648edf86","tid":1906533,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96260d5810643daa9043cc8abd2434f877a8388b","tid":1906533,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:18:05.000Z","msg":"Ok型嘅..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:22:06.000Z","msg":"黑轉粉?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T04:22:56.000Z","msg":"好好地對女友都好過周圍做狗公嘅"},{"pid":"abec103bafa23732453acfa312c91d5f90bfffc2","tid":1906